{"id":60976,"date":"2024-11-21T12:58:38","date_gmt":"2024-11-21T07:28:38","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=60976"},"modified":"2024-11-27T10:34:28","modified_gmt":"2024-11-27T05:04:28","slug":"small-coffee-table-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/small-coffee-table-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Upgrade Your Living Space With These 10 Small Coffee Tables"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Explore stylish small coffee tables for small spaces<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Have you ever wondered how a single piece of furniture can completely transform a small living space? The small coffee table is a humble game-changer for maximising both style and functionality. Whether you are dealing with a cosy apartment, a compact balcony, or a snug living room, finding the right coffee table can make all the difference.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This blog will explore a variety of small coffee tables that fit perfectly into tight spaces while enhancing your decor. From sleek modern designs to charming wooden pieces, we have got something for every taste and need. So, let&#8217;s dive in and discover the ideal coffee table to complement your living space layout. Read on!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. The Living Room Small Coffee Table is an All-Purpose Essential<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A living room (small) coffee table can be the centrepiece of your space without overwhelming it. Go for designs that blend functionality and style, such as a compact <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/coffee-table-design-with-storage\/\">coffee table with built-in storage<\/a> or a sleek, minimalist design.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122654\/living-room-all-purpose-small-coffee-table.jpg\" alt=\"Compact living room coffee table with built-in storage, combining functionality and minimalist design.\" class=\"wp-image-60987\" style=\"width:838px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122654\/living-room-all-purpose-small-coffee-table.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122654\/living-room-all-purpose-small-coffee-table-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122654\/living-room-all-purpose-small-coffee-table-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122654\/living-room-all-purpose-small-coffee-table-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Blend functionality and style in your home<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. Get a Corner Fix With a Perfect Small Round Coffee Table<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A small <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/round-coffee-table-design-ideas\/\">round coffee table<\/a> is ideal for tight corners and smaller living spaces. Its curved edges make it safer for homes with children and pets while adding a touch of sophistication. This type of table can also help soften the angles in a room, making it feel more inviting.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122625\/corner-fix-perfect-small-round-coffee-table.jpg\" alt=\"Small round coffee table with curved edges, perfect for tight corners and safe for homes with children and pets.\" class=\"wp-image-60984\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122625\/corner-fix-perfect-small-round-coffee-table.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122625\/corner-fix-perfect-small-round-coffee-table-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122625\/corner-fix-perfect-small-round-coffee-table-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122625\/corner-fix-perfect-small-round-coffee-table-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Round coffee table softens the room angles<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">3. Small Wood Coffee Table for an Inviting Earthy Charm<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Nothing beats the timeless beauty of a small wood coffee table. Whether you prefer oak, walnut, or pine, a wooden coffee table can bring warmth and character to your living space. It&#8217;s a versatile piece that can complement both modern and traditional interiors.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122723\/small-wood-coffee-table-for-an-inviting-earthy-charm.jpg\" alt=\"Small wooden coffee table made of oak, walnut, or pine, adding warmth and timeless charm to modern or traditional interiors.\" class=\"wp-image-60990\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122723\/small-wood-coffee-table-for-an-inviting-earthy-charm.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122723\/small-wood-coffee-table-for-an-inviting-earthy-charm-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122723\/small-wood-coffee-table-for-an-inviting-earthy-charm-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122723\/small-wood-coffee-table-for-an-inviting-earthy-charm-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Wooden furniture is perfect for adding warmth to any room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">4. Experience Coffee Bliss in Nature With a Small Coffee Table for Balcony<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Turn your balcony into a cosy cafe-like retreat with a small coffee table for balcony settings. The tables for this space are designed to be compact yet stylish, making them perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or evening drinks outdoors.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122556\/coffee-bliss-in-nature-with-a-small-coffee-table-for-balcony.jpg\" alt=\"Small coffee table for balcony, blending with nature, compact and stylish, perfect for coffee or evening drinks outdoors.\" class=\"wp-image-60981\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122556\/coffee-bliss-in-nature-with-a-small-coffee-table-for-balcony.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122556\/coffee-bliss-in-nature-with-a-small-coffee-table-for-balcony-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122556\/coffee-bliss-in-nature-with-a-small-coffee-table-for-balcony-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122556\/coffee-bliss-in-nature-with-a-small-coffee-table-for-balcony-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Plants connect homes to nature<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">5. Compact Coffee Table: Big on Style, Small in Size<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When space is at a premium, a mini coffee table can provide just the right amount of surface area without taking up too much room. These pint-sized tables come in various designs, from mid-century modern to industrial chic. They fit in any space; you can use them to display your cute decor items or leave them as is.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122616\/compact-coffee-table-big-on-style-small-in-size.jpg\" alt=\"Mini coffee table in mid-century modern or industrial style, perfect for small spaces to display decor or maximize functionality\" class=\"wp-image-60983\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122616\/compact-coffee-table-big-on-style-small-in-size.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122616\/compact-coffee-table-big-on-style-small-in-size-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122616\/compact-coffee-table-big-on-style-small-in-size-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122616\/compact-coffee-table-big-on-style-small-in-size-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Land a big style punch in a small package<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">6. Multifunctional Wins: Small Coffee Tables With Chairs!<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A small coffee table with chairs can be an excellent choice for an all-in-one solution. This furniture set is perfect for hosting guests or enjoying a casual meal, making it a practical addition to any living space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122645\/heart-on-multifunctional-furniture-small-coffee-tables-with-chairs-are-ideal.jpg\" alt=\"Small coffee table with chairs, a multifunctional set ideal for hosting guests or enjoying casual meals in compact spaces.\" class=\"wp-image-60986\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122645\/heart-on-multifunctional-furniture-small-coffee-tables-with-chairs-are-ideal.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122645\/heart-on-multifunctional-furniture-small-coffee-tables-with-chairs-are-ideal-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122645\/heart-on-multifunctional-furniture-small-coffee-tables-with-chairs-are-ideal-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122645\/heart-on-multifunctional-furniture-small-coffee-tables-with-chairs-are-ideal-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A query corner lamp grabs eyeballs<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">7. An Attractive Small, Low Round Coffee Table&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A small modern coffee table can create a cosy and intimate seating area. Its low profile makes it perfect for lounging on floor cushions or a low sofa, and the round shape adds a soft touch to your decor.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122607\/coffee-with-drama-small-low-round-coffee-table.jpg\" alt=\"Small, low round coffee table with a modern design, perfect for floor seating or low sofas, adding a cosy touch to your decor.\" class=\"wp-image-60982\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122607\/coffee-with-drama-small-low-round-coffee-table.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122607\/coffee-with-drama-small-low-round-coffee-table-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122607\/coffee-with-drama-small-low-round-coffee-table-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122607\/coffee-with-drama-small-low-round-coffee-table-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">8. Small Nesting Coffee Tables Serve All Homes<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>These small coffee tables for small spaces are a brilliant solution for those who crave flexibility and style in their living spaces. These sets typically include two or more tables of different sizes that can be stacked together or used separately, offering a versatile furniture option that adapts to your needs.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122715\/small-nesting-coffee-tables-serve-perfect-proportions.jpg\" alt=\"Small nesting coffee tables in versatile sets, ideal for small spaces, offering flexibility and style with stackable or separate use.\" class=\"wp-image-60989\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122715\/small-nesting-coffee-tables-serve-perfect-proportions.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122715\/small-nesting-coffee-tables-serve-perfect-proportions-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122715\/small-nesting-coffee-tables-serve-perfect-proportions-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122715\/small-nesting-coffee-tables-serve-perfect-proportions-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Nesting tables are perfect for small apartments<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Fresh ideas to brighten up your kitchen & mood!\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/18110451\/fresh-ideas-brighten-up-kitchen-and-mood.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">9. A Small Coffee Table With Storage Keeps Spaces Neat<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Small coffee tables with storage are a practical choice for tidying your living area. These tables often feature drawers, shelves, or hidden compartments where you can stow away magazines, remote controls, and other essentials.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122703\/small-coffee-table-with-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Small coffee table with storage, featuring drawers or hidden compartments to keep living spaces neat and organized.\" class=\"wp-image-60988\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122703\/small-coffee-table-with-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122703\/small-coffee-table-with-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122703\/small-coffee-table-with-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122703\/small-coffee-table-with-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A tidy living area<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">10. Personalise Your Space With DIY Small Coffee Table Ideas<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For those who love a hands-on project, DIY small coffee table ideas can be a great way to personalise your living space. The possibilities are endless, from repurposing old crates to building a table from scratch.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122636\/DIY-small-coffee-table-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"DIY small coffee table ideas for personalizing your space, from repurposing crates to building a custom table.\" class=\"wp-image-60985\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122636\/DIY-small-coffee-table-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122636\/DIY-small-coffee-table-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122636\/DIY-small-coffee-table-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/25122636\/DIY-small-coffee-table-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Repurpose old materials to build a DIY coffee table<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>To sum up, selecting the right small coffee table can significantly enhance the functionality and aesthetic of any living space. Whether a small hardwood coffee table or a small square glass coffee table with a low-profile design, the key is to balance style and practicality. By considering dimensions, shape, and style trends, you can find a coffee table that complements your room perfectly. Remember, a well-chosen coffee table serves as a beauty spot and maximises space, enmeshing your home in a warm aroma. So, relax and sip your coffee in style. Explore a wide range of options right here:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, Read about <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/lift-top-coffee-table\/\">Lift-Top Coffee Table Ideas For Your Living Room<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>FAQs<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1. What shape coffee table is best for small spaces?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Round and oval coffee tables are best for small spaces because they lack sharp corners, which allows for better flow and movement. These shapes also help create the illusion of more space and make the room feel more open and inviting.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>2. What are the small coffee table dimensions?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Small coffee tables typically range from 30 to 36 inches in length, 18 to 24 inches in width, and 16 to 18 inches in height. These dimensions make them suitable for compact living areas while still providing sufficient surface space for everyday use.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>3. Are low coffee tables in style?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes, low coffee tables are currently in style. They offer a modern and minimalist aesthetic, making them popular in contemporary and Scandinavian interior designs. Their lower profile also creates a more open and spacious feel in a room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>4. What table makes a room look bigger?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Glass coffee tables make a room look bigger due to their transparency, which creates a sense of openness and unobstructed space. Additionally, tables with slim, minimalistic designs and legs elevate the table off the floor, enhancing the perception of more room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>5. Should the coffee table be smaller than the sofa?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes, a coffee table should be smaller than the sofa. Ideally, it should be about two-thirds the length of the sofa and proportionate in height. This ensures a balanced look and maintains adequate space for movement around the table and seating area.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\